<p>This says: "Hey serializer, don't serialize <em>any</em> properties by default,
just hang out in your pajamas". Now we'll use <code>@Serializer\Expose()</code> to 
whitelist the stuff we <em>do</em> want. We don't want <code>id</code> - so leave that. 
Above the <code>$name</code> property, add <code>@Serializer\Expose()</code>. Do this same thing 
above <code>$avatarNumber</code>, <code>$tagLine</code> and <code>$powerLevel</code>:</p>
